		<h2>Change log</h2>
		<div class="changeLog">
		<strong>Version 1.0.9</strong>
		<ul>
			<li>Support for <a href="http://jspm.io/">JSPM</a></li>
		</ul>
		<strong>Version 1.0.8</strong>
		<ul>
			<li>Added isClosable check for rows and columns</li>
