		<ul>
			<li>Configuration for new windows is now passed through localStorage rather than URL parameter {{issue 23}}</li>
			<li>{{issue 23}} also closes the XSS attack vector created by passing config through the url which fixes {{issue 28}}</li>
			<li>Allow empty dashboards {{issue 24}}</li>
			<li>Fixed resizing bug for maximised components {{issue 25}}</li>
			<li>Added strip-tags for title in popout windows. Also removed XSS filtering since configuration is now safely passed through localStorage (see {{issue 23}}). {{issue 18}}</li>
		</ul>
		<strong>Version 1.0.5</strong>
		<ul>
			<li>Added basic touch event support {{issue 4}}</li>
			<li>Fixed state change on DragProxy bug {{issue 15}}</li>
			<li>Added support for reorderEnabled attribute on an item level {{issue 13}}</li>
		</ul>
		<strong>Version 1.0.4</strong>
		<ul>
			<li>Full support for HTML in title attributes / tabs {{issue 6}}</li>
			<li>Middle mouse button now closes tab {{issue 7}}</li>
			<li>layout emits 'tabCreated' event for every tab {{issue 6}}</li>
			<li>Added support for empty stacks {{issue 5}}</li>
			<li>'isClosable: false' now prevents item from being destroyed if it is the only child of its parent {{issue 5}}</li>
		</ul>
